<section class="about grainy" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container about-inner">

    <div class="about-roles">
      <span class="label role-chip">Product Engineer</span>
      <span class="role-separator" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
      <span class="label role-chip">Frontend Lead</span>
    </div>

    <div class="about-bio">
      <p>
        Building intuitive software end-to-end is what I do best! From defining
        the problem to shipping scalable solutions, I've got a sharp product
        sense, a strong Angular expertise, and a relentless focus on eliminating
        friction.
      </p>
      <p>
        Driven by a passion for mentoring and empowering others. As a team lead
        and product owner, I've balanced the management of other engineers with
        my own individual contributions, always keeping the user's experience at
        the center of every decision.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background-color: var(--slate);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-roles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .role-chip {
    color: var(--pale-cyan);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  }

  .role-separator {
    color: var(--light-blue);
    opacity: 0.4;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .about-bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-bio p {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.3vw, 1.02rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-roles {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
